   "source": [
    "## Datapreprocessing\n",
    "### . Lower case\n",
    "### . Tokenization\n",
    "### . Removing special characters\n",
    "### . Removing slop words and punctuation\n",
    "### . Stemming"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 41,
   "id": "3e5f2508-339e-429f-95ce-83d12864995b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def transform_text(text):\n",
    "    text = text.lower()\n",
    "    text = nltk.word_tokenize(text) # tokenize\n",
    "\n",
    "    y = []\n",
    "    for i in text:              # removing special character\n",
    "        if i.isalnum():\n",
    "            y.append(i)\n",
    "            \n",
    "    text = y[:]\n",
    "    y.clear()\n",
    "\n",
    "    for i in text:\n",
    "         if i not in stopwords.words('english') and i not in string.punctuation:\n",
    "             y.append(i)\n",
    "\n",
    "    text = y[:]\n",
    "    y.clear()\n",
    "\n",
    "    for i in text:\n",
    "        y.append(ps.stem(i))\n",
    "\n",
    "    return \" \".join(y)"
   ]
  },
